@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BackofficeOperator
participant ":System" as System

activate BackofficeOperator

BackofficeOperator -> System : Requests to register an aircraft engine model

activate System
System --> BackofficeOperator : Requests engine model data
deactivate System

BackofficeOperator -> System : Provides engine model data

activate System
System --> System : Check if Backoffice Operator is authorized
System --> System : Validate required data
System --> System : Validate manufacturer
System --> System : Validate engine type
System --> System : Validate power
System --> System : Validate fuel type
System --> System : Validate efficiency
System --> System : Check model name and manufacturer uniqueness

alt engine model data is valid
    System --> System : Register aircraft engine model
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Aircraft engine model registered successfully
else engine model data is invalid
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate BackofficeOperator

@enduml